* Good portfolio of previous work, including on GitHub portfolio, and good references from past clients and managers
* Solid grasp of multiple programming languages, including mastery of one or more
* Demonstrated interest in the software world, including awareness of and opinions on new developments
* Ability to explain complex concepts in simple terms
* Cultural fit with the startup, including with the engineering team specifically
* Passion for the startup's mission to ensure intrinsic motivation
* Fizz Buzz Test! [Fizz Buzz Test](http://c2.com/cgi/wiki?FizzBuzzTest)
